<b>Lanys T'yvl</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/upatofnaud.showPublicProfile?language=EN>patofnaud</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/7/01 2:31:32 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Can I Still Do My Epic? please reply=)</span><hr size=1> Nope you got it right.<br>
