Sneak is basically a faction change to INDIFF if you are BEHIND the NPC/MOB. BEHIND varies from mob to mob but usually anything a bit more than line of sight is considered behind..<br>
<br>
Just be away, some mobs arbitrarily will turn to a person they are transacting with. If that happens, you are toast. <p><body lang=EN-US style='tab-interval:.5in'>

